wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked:
'''Indangakintu (IP) yawe [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|yahagaritswe kuri wiki zose]].'''

Guhagarikwa vyakozwe na $1 ($2).
Imvo yatanzwe ni ''$3''.

* Guhagarikwa vyatanguye: $4
* Guhagarikwa bizorangira: $5

Indangakintu (IP) yawe y'ubu ni $6.
Usabwe gushira insiguro zose ziri musi mubibazo vyose usaba.

Mugihe wibaza ko woba wahagaritwe kubwo kwihenda, ushobora gusanga inkuru z'inyongera n'amabwirizwa muri [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|Nta proxies zuguruye]] indinganizo rusangi.
atari ukwo naho, kuyaga k'uguhagarikwa, gerageza [[m:Steward requests/Global|rungika kuri Meta-Wiki igisabo co gusubiramwo]].
